contribute networking technologies and system management software. TCE will
draw upon its consumer products, compression and decoder technologies.
The Sun-TCE venture will compete directly with the marketing alliance
announced by Digital Equipment and General Instrument, which is similarly
aimed at providing 'end-to-end interactive video system solutions'.
The jointly marketed systems will include Digital's video interactive
information technology and GI's encryption and decoder technologies.
