FT  12 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Cairn Energy cuts US holding
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cairn Energy, the oil and gas exploration and production company, has placed
824,000 shares in Cairn Energy USA raising a net Pounds 3.9m.
As a result, Cairn now holds about 54 per cent of CEUSA.
Cairn expects to sell further CEUSA shares in a US placing dependent on the
proposed acquisition of US oil and gas interests of Aeneas Group by CEUSA.
